extracted_metadata.title: Jerusalem Interfaith Webinar! Israeli and Palestinian religious leaders unite for PEACE
extracted_metadata.description: A follow up webinar to our 2024 interfaith march for human rights and peace, which took place in Jerusalem in June, 2024. Speakers include: David Goren, Jonathan Khuttab, Ghadir Hani, Rabanit Leah Shakdiel.
